 For numbers from 1 to N:
 If number is divisible by 3 → print "Fizz"
 If divisible by 5 → print "Buzz"
 If divisible by both 3 and 5 → print "FizzBuzz"
 Otherwise → print the number itself

program:
num = int(input())
for i in range(1, num+1):
    if i % 3 == 0 and i % 5 == 0:
        print("FizzBuzz")
    elif i % 3 == 0:
        print("Fizz")
    elif i % 5 == 0:
        print("Buzz")
    
    else:
        print(i)
